Police said that he was being sought in connection with crimes committed in Steenberg and Grassy Park. CAPE TOWN - Police in Wynberg are searching for a man who is wanted in connection with rape and sexual assault. The suspect has been identified as 64-year-old Jonathan Arends. Police said that he was being sought in connection with crimes committed in Steenberg and Grassy Park. The police's Noloyiso Rwexana: "He hangs around the Steenberg area. A warrant for his arrest was issued and we appeal to the public for anyone who knows his whereabouts to contact the investigating officers on 021 799 1315."